folder: Flatbush Avenue & Price Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Flatbush Avenue Extension, north from Prince Street (right). The bridge, with the elevated train thereon,
is on Myrtle Avenue.
September 6, 1939
P. L. Sperr

folder: Flatbush Avenue & Willoughby Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Flatbush Avenue Extension, at the S. W. corner of Willoughby Street, showing Green's used-car sales depot. The trolley tracks are on Willoughby Street, running across
Flatbush Avenue Extension.
April 17, 1940
L. Sperr
